author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Hand protection tips…I have to work around ductwork which can easily slice a hand. But I also need grip to use different materials and tools. I like wearing the @ironclad_gloves microfoam nitrile dotted gloves for projects like this. The gloves have ANSI A5 cut resistance which make them a perfect fit for mixed use projects. Many thanks to Ironclad for partnering with me and making gloves that keep hands safe🔥#handprotection #workgloves #ironcladgloves #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
